---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="About Wipp">
  
  <script type="module" src="https://unpkg.com/@splinetool/viewer@1.9.59/build/spline-viewer.js"></script>

  <section class="relative min-h-[90vh] flex items-center justify-center overflow-hidden pt-20">
    
    <div class="absolute inset-0 z-0 opacity-60 dark:opacity-80">
      <spline-viewer url="https://prod.spline.design/6Wq1Q7YGyM-iab9i/scene.splinecode"></spline-viewer>
    </div>
    
    <div class="relative z-10 text-center max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6 pointer-events-none">
      <div class="inline-block px-4 py-1.5 rounded-full border border-neutral-200 dark:border-neutral-700 bg-white/50 dark:bg-black/50 backdrop-blur-md mb-6 animate-fade-in-up">
        <span class="text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-neutral-500 dark:text-neutral-400">The Future of Creative Growth</span>
      </div>
      
      <h1 class="text-6xl md:text-8xl font-bold tracking-tighter text-neutral-900 dark:text-white mb-6 animate-fade-in-up delay-100">
        Less Noise.<br />
        <span class="text-transparent bg-clip-text bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-600 to-violet-600">More Signal.</span>
      </h1>
      
      <p class="text-xl md:text-2xl text-neutral-600 dark:text-neutral-300 max-w-2xl mx-auto leading-relaxed animate-fade-in-up delay-200">
        Wipp is a community-first platform for artists who care about conversation over clout.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="absolute bottom-0 left-0 w-full h-32 bg-gradient-to-t from-white dark:from-black to-transparent z-10"></div>
  </section>

  <section class="py-32 px-6 bg-white dark:bg-black relative z-20">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto text-center">
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-5xl font-bold leading-tight text-neutral-900 dark:text-white mb-12">
        Most platforms are broken.<br/>
        <span class="text-neutral-400 dark:text-neutral-600">We built the fix.</span>
      </h2>
      
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8 text-left">
        <div class="p-8 rounded-3xl bg-neutral-50 dark:bg-neutral-900 border border-neutral-100 dark:border-neutral-800 hover:-translate-y-2 transition-transform duration-500">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-blue-100 dark:bg-blue-900/30 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-2xl mb-4">üí¨</div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-2 dark:text-white">Real Feedback</h3>
          <p class="text-neutral-500">Stop posting into the void. Get thoughtful critiques that actually help you grow.</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="p-8 rounded-3xl bg-neutral-50 dark:bg-neutral-900 border border-neutral-100 dark:border-neutral-800 hover:-translate-y-2 transition-transform duration-500 delay-100">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-purple-100 dark:bg-purple-900/30 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-2xl mb-4">üö´</div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-2 dark:text-white">No Algorithms</h3>
          <p class="text-neutral-500">We don't sell your attention. No pay-to-win exposure. No follower farming.</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="p-8 rounded-3xl bg-neutral-50 dark:bg-neutral-900 border border-neutral-100 dark:border-neutral-800 hover:-translate-y-2 transition-transform duration-500 delay-200">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-green-100 dark:bg-green-900/30 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-2xl mb-4">üå±</div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-2 dark:text-white">Pure Growth</h3>
          <p class="text-neutral-500">Inspired by Reddit's depth and Behance's visuals. Built for artists, not ads.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="py-20 px-6 bg-neutral-50 dark:bg-neutral-900/50">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto">
      <div class="mb-16 text-center">
        <h2 class="text-4xl font-bold text-neutral-900 dark:text-white mb-4">Why Wipp Exists</h2>
        <p class="text-neutral-500">The anti-social media platform.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-4 grid-rows-2 gap-4 h-auto md:h-[600px]">
        
        <div class="md:col-span-2 md:row-span-2 bg-white dark:bg-neutral-900 p-8 rounded-3xl border border-neutral-200 dark:border-neutral-800 flex flex-col justify-between overflow-hidden relative group">
          <div class="relative z-10">
            <h3 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-4 dark:text-white">Community First</h3>
            <p class="text-neutral-500 text-lg">Discussions matter more than likes. Visibility comes from contribution, not popularity. We are building a home, not a billboard.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="absolute -right-10 -bottom-10 w-64 h-64 bg-gradient-to-br from-blue-500 to-purple-600 rounded-full blur-3xl opacity-20 group-hover:opacity-40 transition-opacity"></div>
        </div>

        <div class="md:col-span-2 bg-black text-white p-8 rounded-3xl border border-neutral-800 flex items-center justify-between relative overflow-hidden group">
          <div>
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-2">No Ads. No Tricks.</h3>
            <p class="text-neutral-400">We don't sell your data.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="text-4xl grayscale group-hover:grayscale-0 transition-all">üîí</div>
        </div>

        <div class="md:col-span-1 bg-white dark:bg-neutral-900 p-8 rounded-3xl border border-neutral-200 dark:border-neutral-800 flex flex-col justify-center text-center hover:bg-neutral-50 dark:hover:bg-neutral-800 transition-colors">
          <div class="text-4xl mb-4">üé®</div>
          <h3 class="font-bold dark:text-white">For Creators</h3>
          <p class="text-xs text-neutral-500 mt-2">Digital, Traditional, 3D, Motion.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="md:col-span-1 bg-white dark:bg-neutral-900 p-8 rounded-3xl border border-neutral-200 dark:border-neutral-800 flex flex-col justify-center text-center hover:bg-neutral-50 dark:hover:bg-neutral-800 transition-colors">
           <div class="text-4xl mb-4">ü§ù</div>
           <h3 class="font-bold dark:text-white">Safe Space</h3>
           <p class="text-xs text-neutral-500 mt-2">No flex culture. Just art.</p>
        </div>

      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="py-32 px-6 bg-white dark:bg-black">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto">
      <h2 class="text-4xl font-bold text-center mb-16 dark:text-white">Common Questions</h2>

      <div class="space-y-4">
        
        <details class="group bg-neutral-50 dark:bg-neutral-900 rounded-2xl p-6 [&_summary::-webkit-details-marker]:hidden cursor-pointer">
          <summary class="flex items-center justify-between font-bold text-lg dark:text-white">
            Is Wipp free to use?
            <span class="transition group-open:rotate-180">
              <svg fill="none" height="24" shape-rendering="geometricPrecision" stroke="currentColor" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="24"><path d="M6 9l6 6 6-6"></path></svg>
            </span>
          </summary>
          <p class="text-neutral-500 mt-4 group-open:animate-fadeIn">
            Yes. Posting, browsing, and participating in the community is completely free. Optional paid features may exist in the future to support the platform, but core access will always remain free.
          </p>
        </details>

        <details class="group bg-neutral-50 dark:bg-neutral-900 rounded-2xl p-6 [&_summary::-webkit-details-marker]:hidden cursor-pointer">
          <summary class="flex items-center justify-between font-bold text-lg dark:text-white">
            Who owns my content?
            <span class="transition group-open:rotate-180">
              <svg fill="none" height="24" shape-rendering="geometricPrecision" stroke="currentColor" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="24"><path d="M6 9l6 6 6-6"></path></svg>
            </span>
          </summary>
          <p class="text-neutral-500 mt-4 group-open:animate-fadeIn">
            You do. You always retain 100% ownership of your work. Wipp only displays your content to enable community discussion. You can delete your account and data at any time.
          </p>
        </details>

        <details class="group bg-neutral-50 dark:bg-neutral-900 rounded-2xl p-6 [&_summary::-webkit-details-marker]:hidden cursor-pointer">
          <summary class="flex items-center justify-between font-bold text-lg dark:text-white">
            Is AI content allowed?
            <span class="transition group-open:rotate-180">
              <svg fill="none" height="24" shape-rendering="geometricPrecision" stroke="currentColor" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="24"><path d="M6 9l6 6 6-6"></path></svg>
            </span>
          </summary>
          <p class="text-neutral-500 mt-4 group-open:animate-fadeIn">
            Low-effort AI spam is not allowed. AI-assisted work may be discussed only if clearly labeled and used responsibly. The focus of Wipp is human creativity and learning.
          </p>
        </details>

        <details class="group bg-neutral-50 dark:bg-neutral-900 rounded-2xl p-6 [&_summary::-webkit-details-marker]:hidden cursor-pointer">
          <summary class="flex items-center justify-between font-bold text-lg dark:text-white">
            How do I get visibility?
            <span class="transition group-open:rotate-180">
              <svg fill="none" height="24" shape-rendering="geometricPrecision" stroke="currentColor" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="24"><path d="M6 9l6 6 6-6"></path></svg>
            </span>
          </summary>
          <p class="text-neutral-500 mt-4 group-open:animate-fadeIn">
            There are no follower-based algorithms here. Work gains visibility through thoughtful feedback, community engagement, and meaningful discussion.
          </p>
        </details>

      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="py-20 text-center border-t border-neutral-100 dark:border-neutral-800">
    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-6 dark:text-white">Ready to join the conversation?</h2>
    <div class="flex gap-4 justify-center">
      <a href="/explore" class="bg-black dark:bg-white text-white dark:text-black px-8 py-3 rounded-full font-bold hover:scale-105 transition-transform">Explore Wipp</a>
    </div>
  </section>

</BaseLayout>

<style>
  /* Custom Animations */
  .animate-fade-in-up {
    animation: fadeInUp 0.8s cubic-bezier(0.16, 1, 0.3, 1) forwards;
    opacity: 0;
    transform: translateY(20px);
  }
  
  .delay-100 { animation-delay: 100ms; }
  .delay-200 { animation-delay: 200ms; }

  @keyframes fadeInUp {
    from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(20px); }
    to { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
  }
  
  @keyframes fadeIn {
    from { opacity: 0; }
    to { opacity: 1; }
  }
</style>